window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>After a rather eventful visit to Timbermere, Valdis Wolfbane and his companions have returned to the farm. Their goal is clear: turn their little piece of land into something halfway close to self-sufficient.</p> <p>Thankfully, with a dark elf's nature magic and the cooking skills of a former huntress, the farm's prospects couldn't be better.</p> <p>There's a meeting with the town's beautiful mayoress to look forward to, as well as a friendly visit from a mage with a few spells short of a grimoire.</p> <p>Truly, the life of a farmer isn't without its ups and downs, but it's a sure sight better than the life he left behind.</p> <p>After all, the only corpses left behind are kale stems.</p>"; 
